## What Nimbus Is Not
- Not a SaaS product ŌĆö no Nimbus cloud, no Nimbus account, no Nimbus server
- Not a consumer app ŌĆö built for technically literate users
- Not a prototype ŌĆö every interface is held to production standards
- Not a macOS-first app ŌĆö platform equality is mechanically enforced by CI
